          "raw_text": "1Combine vinegar, garlic, salt, cumin, and pepper in a large nonreactive bowl. While whisking constantly, slowly add oil in a thin stream until completely incorporated; set aside."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "10dc041f-b189-404f-9010-613273b27862",
